      <div class="feature-card" onclick="addRipple(event,this)"><div class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div><div class="feature-title">Community Safety</div><div class="feature-desc">Shared alerts empower entire communities to prepare and respond faster to flood events.</div></div>
